CHANGES
=======

14.3.0
------

* OVN DBs clustering
* Change default for NovaNfsVersion to NFSv4.2
* Disable postcopy for ovn/ovs-dpdk
* Default ganesha-internal service endpoint to external network
* Enabling vhost-postcopy-support when live\_migration\_permit\_post\_copy
* Add CephAdmDebug parameter
* Make memcached port parameters globally available
* Do not fail if haproxy container UUID changes
* nova-compute: Adding failed\_when to nova-compute stop task
* Wire up renamed upgrade periodic template
* Remove all docker related tasks from upgrades
* Remove leftover of hieradata cleanup
* Role parameter for tripleo\_kernel\_defer\_reboot
* vncproxy: removal of tags and steps change from post\_upgrade\_tasks
* Do not log amphora ssh keys
* Add OS version to check reboot happened
* Introducing the ComputeVdpa role
* Test override of CephClusterName in 004 standalone
* Add tool to convert net-data from v1 to v2
* Enable image copy for multiple RBD Glance stores

14.2.0
------

* Enable proxy header parsing in Octavia API
* Fix manila-cephfsganesha-config environment for cephadm
* Make default of NeutronDefaultAvailabilityZones empty array
* FFU: change transfer parameters for database resync
* Wire up the tripleo-upgrades-wallaby-pipeline
* Moves undercloud upgrade introspection data migration to step 1
* Simplify libvirt/qemu ssl certificates
* Neutron: Use the pids subsystem to look up container id
* Adjust enable-stf.yaml for latest recommendations
* Support cinder image conversion on an NFS share
* Get roles data from stack output on UC upgrade
* Add THT Jinja2 data sources as stack output
* Enable DPDK OVS PMD Auto Load Balance
* Remove NovaVncProxyNetwork from ServiceNetMap
* Move designate from experimental
* Support additional IP so bind and unbound can collocate
* Extend UC ephemeral heat to export network
* Pass scripts list for download for sensubility
* Simplify nova service  templates
* Support for OVS DPDK pmd auto balance parameters
* Do not run Swift rsync container in single replica mode
* Add Ephemeral Heat service
* Add network-v2 default files + vip data examples
* Move scenario004 to cephadm
* Always run network config for undercloud
* Fix NetworkDeploymentActionValue format
* Add support for keystone\_authtoken/memcache\_use\_advanced\_pool
* Set tripleo\_cephadm rbd mirror vars
* Limit collectds memory usage
* Introduce nova virtlogd wrapper
* Set OS\_CLOUD instead in stackrc
* Revert "Always run network config for undercloud"
* Revert "Always run network config for undercloud"
* Remove heat::heat\_keystone\_clients\_url definition
* Add post\_upgrade\_task and remove puppet-ceph pkg
* Always run network config for undercloud
* Ignore puppet\_config is an empty dict
* Switch barbican actions to use kolla\_config
* Fix typo that breaks Octavia db sync step
* Use kolla\_config for other actions
* Add glance db purge job
* Make UpgradeLeappDevelSkip per-role
* Use community.general ansible collection instead of modules
* Refactor OVN bridge MAC addresses
* Bump ovs and ovn versions to 2.15 for FFWD
* Fix broken restart of ovndb\_server during minor update
* Set ganesha idmap.conf file path and overrides
* Add alertmanager port parameter
* HA minor update: fix bad pcs invocation
* Cleanup optional flag for conf.modules.d
* Fix container security\_opts type

14.1.2
------

* Pass custom CephConfigPath parameter to ceph-nfs role
* Update rhsm repo examples for RHEL8 deployments
* Add OS::TripleO::UndercloudUpgradeEphemeralHeat
* Fix typo in ceilometer-write-qdr environment file
* Add param for RBD disk cache modes
* set ganesha idmap.conf file path and overrides
* Fix cinder's cephx keyring file permissions
* Allow customizing podman's [engine]/events\_logger
* Include the standalone ganesha tasks when ceph is external
* Disable tunnelled migration
* Added the posibility of skipping the NFS ping test on the rear installation
* Add environment for external network VIP
* Add OVNCMSOptions to Controller and Networker roles
* Add option for enabling rsyslog reopenOnTruncate
* Remove Ceph cluster replica and PG num from low-memory-usage.yaml
* Skip cephadm playbook when there is no mon or nfs group
* Expose the monitoring\_stack network to cephadm
* Use collection FQCN for podman modules
* Fix network\_cidrs when ManageNetworks: false
* libvirt: fix formatting of the log\_outputs parameter
* Move ceph\_admin\_extra\_vars logic to tripleo-ansible
* Make clustercheck service accessible over socat
* Add neutron port tag hint for role name
* Introduce CephHciOsdCount and CephHciOsdType
* Re-add NovaVncProxyNetwork to service\_net\_map.j2.yaml

14.1.1
------

* Disable tunneled mode when use\_tls\_for\_live\_migration
* Don't add external tasks for roles with zero count
* CI - Add vip\_data file
* Add openstack-tox-tht to the gate
* Fix RoleParameters in tuned-baremetal-ansible.yaml
* Stop handler flush
* Don't assume every role has default\_route\_networks
* Update TOX\_CONSTRAINTS\_FILE for stable/wallaby
* Update .gitreview for stable/wallaby

14.1.0
------

* nova: Default to the unversioned q35 machine type on x86\_64
* Make sure the container configuration is refreshed during update
* Default CephClientConfigVars within --working-dir
* Define the GaneshaNetwork parameter used by cephadm
* Fix etcd/tls-e deployments
* Add OVNEncapType option to the ovn controller template
* Remove Keepalived service
* Disable global\_id reclaim for Ceph mons in scenario001
* Simplify manila, memcached and logging services
* Simplify keystone, iscsid service templates
* Simplify cephadm service templates
* Correct metrics\_qdr logging path and regex parsing
* Stop using (and breaking) /var/tmp for horizon temporary things
* Migrate nova cron parameters to NovaApi service
* Fix random redeploy failure during certificate extraction
* Simplify horizon, ipservices templates
* Simplify haproxy service templates
* Don't create/configure swift\_temp\_url\_key
* Add DefaultRoute to deployed\_port.j2
* Update undercloud TLS template with proper keytab group
* Remove EXPERIMENTAL from ovn/sriov env file
* cinder: remove support for the Veritas HyperScale driver
* ScaleIO: Fix outdate template path
* Glance: Fix wrong indent about healthcheck key
* Make SkipRhelEnforcement boolean
* Add CinderBackupCompressionAlgorithm parameter
* Add manila db purge job
* Aodh: define authtoken parameters in AodhApi service
* Add RootStackName to group\_vars
* Deploy RGW by default when cephadm environment is included
* Migrate introspection data for undercloud upgrade
* Use CephRgwCertificateKeySize, not CephCertificateKeySize, for RGW
* Remove deprecated CinderBackendDellEMCXTREMIOIscsi
* Simplify ironic service templates
* Use parameters of the nova::glance class
* Support removing cinder-backup from pcmk control
* Missing client certificate for live-migration with TLS
* Allow access to RabbitMQ management plugin over network
* Add ability to configure glance multiple cinder stores
* Removing duplicate mount point in metrics\_qdr
* Add cinder RBD support for multiple ceph clusters
* Add CinderBackupWorkers and CinderBackupMaxOperations
* Support cinder backups to specific ceph cluster
* Add DefaultRoute parameter to ports/noop.yaml
* Fix "ManageNetworks" use-case
