* Add new options for Barbican PKCS#11 backend
* Add tripleo\_network\_name tag hint to networks
* Set tags on all OS::Neutron::Port resources
* Expose additional network sysctl knobs
* Generate bind pool and bind configuration using deployment info
* Disable RabbitMQ busy-wait for dirty cpu and dirty i/o schedulers
* Remove UndercloudExtraConfig merge\_strategy
* Add some tunable parameters for nova-scheduler
* Disable snapshot support in Cinder NFS backend by default
* nova: Remove versioned default machine types
* Mount /etc/openldap inside the keystone container
