* Revert "Reset sriov\_numvfs to 0 before leapp upgrade"
* Fix swift bare variable warning
* Switch Octavia external tasks to 'post deploy'
* nova: Use LIBGUESTFS\_BACKEND=direct
* Do not loop on ceph\_external\_multi\_config unless it is defined
* Remove pcs/pacemaker package installation from upgrade tasks
* Add sample network data files for network-data-v2
* Add deployed\_port template
* Making sure virt-guest-shutdown.target exists
* Drop python\_cmd set\_Fact
* Add NovaImageTypeExcludeList parameter
* Force json output format for hiera in derive pci whitelist
* Configure OVNCMSOptions=enable-chassis-as-gw within neutron-ovn-sriov.yaml
* Deleting nova-consoleauth services in post-upgrade
* Use Ceph-NFS for Manila in scenario004
* Turn off the etcd TLS workaround used with novajoin
* Add doc/requirements
* Remove useless hieradata for keystone resource management by puppet
* Configure Ceph clients via tripleo-ceph-client (not ceph-ansible)
* Wire up new tripleo upgrades jobs template
* Move the misplaced release note file
* Remove the OVNVifType parameter
* Neutron: Do not set ovn\_l3\_mode
* Rename the template for LoginDefs service
* Remove duplicated tasks to create persisitent directries for haproxy
* Glance: use the puppet parameter to enable image cache feature
* Revert "Move CA cert injection to host\_prep\_tasks"
* Remove ineffective parameters of puppet-rabbitmq
* Serialize shutdown of pacemaker nodes
* Simplify composition of swift-proxy-server pipelines
* Remove unused [ec2]driver parameter
