* Fix Octavia OctaviaTenantLogFacility default
* Implement a Minimal role
* Replace deprecated libvirt\_\* options
* Add ctlplane subnet attrs to group\_vars
* Add ctlplane network attrs to Networks resource output
* Replace bridge\_name and interface\_name in config
* Add attr of networks and subnets to Networks resource
* Add support for Glance disk\_formats configuration
* Add parameters for vTPM feature
* Clear cached facts based on the tag as well
* Refactor OVNMacAddressNetwork
* Remove overcloud\_common.pp
* Configure rsyncd without pid file for Swift
* Use OS::Heat::Value for NetworkConfig
* use os\_net\_config Ansible module to configure networking
* [PowerFlex/VxFlex OS] Fix typos in templates
* enable-ssh-admin: allow to override plan name
* Use consistent naming for MysqlInnodbBufferPoolSize
* Force container fetch
* Check only role path for NetworkConfig
* Remove race during mysql database creation
* Add tripleo-iptables service cleanup
* Rename external network VIP, drop special case
