* Gather more extra stats with the collectd virt plugin
* Adapt container health check for built-in podman health checks

12.6.0
------

* python3-novaclient installation via THT
* Decrease Swift proxy timeouts for GET/HEAD requests
* Complete missing description
* Make sure we noop the Rabbitmq\_ providers
* Make sure we noop the Mysql\_ providers
* Fix Flakes and lower-constraints errors
* Expose new  parameter \`NovaVGPUTypesDeviceAddressesMapping\`
* Change permissions on /run/octavia to octavia
* Replace deprecated nova::compute::ironic::max\_concurrent\_builds
* Update plan-sample to reference new interface
* Update swift rsyslog configuration
